jobDescription.text:
Job Title: Warehouse Packer

We are seeking dedicated individuals who are passionate about delivering excellence in every aspect of their work. As a Warehouse Packer, you will play a vital role in ensuring our products are prepared with precision and care for our valued customers.

Location: Preferred location Atlantic City, NJ.

Roles and Responsibilities:- Accurately pack products for shipment, ensuring quality and consistency.
- Collaborate with team members to meet daily packing and shipping goals.
- Maintain a clean and organized workspace to uphold safety and efficiency.
- Conduct quality checks on products to ensure they meet our high standards.
- Assist in inventory management and restocking as needed.
- Follow all safety protocols and procedures to create a safe working environment.

Experience Level: Preferred experience level is 6 to 10 years.

Desired Skills:We are looking for individuals who possess:

- Strong attention to detail to ensure accuracy in packing and labeling.
- Excellent communication skills to effectively collaborate with colleagues.
- A proactive approach to problem-solving and a willingness to learn.
- Physical stamina and the ability to lift and move heavy items safely.
- Familiarity with warehouse operations and packing procedures.

Employment Type: Direct hire.

Company Description:** TRC Talent Solutions is proud to be an Equal Opportunity Employer (EOE). All qualified applicants will receive consideration for employment without regard to race, color, religion, sex, age, national origin, protected veteran status, disability status, sexual orientation, gender identity or expression, marital status, genetic information, or any other characteristic protected by law.

At TRC, we take pride in fulfilling our opportunity to add value to our clients business as their staffing partner, while working tirelessly to connect thousands of individuals each year with work opportunities where they can meet the needs of their families and have the potential to build their careers.
